utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: I'd like to book a trip to Atlantis from Caprica on Saturday, August 13, 2016 for 8 adults.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: I have a tight budget of 1700.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Hi...I checked a few options for you, and unfortunately, we do not currently have any trips that meet this criteria.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you like to book an alternate travel option?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Yes, how about going to Neverland from Caprica on August 13, 2016 for 5 adults.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: For this trip, my budget would be 1900.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I checked the availability for this date and there were no trips available.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you like to select some alternate dates?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: I have no flexibility for dates... but I can leave from Atlantis rather than Caprica.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: How about that?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I checked the availability for that date and there were no trips available.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you like to select some alternate dates?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: I suppose I'll speak with my husband to see if we can choose other dates, and then I'll come back to you.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Thanks for your help

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Hello there i am looking to go on a vacation with my family to Gotham City, can you help me?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: when  would you like to travel and how many people will you be?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Not sure when we want to leave, but we are 12 kids and 5 adults

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: do you have a budget?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: yes i do, it is around $2200

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: where will you be travelling from?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: We are from Neverland

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: We have nothing available leaving from Neverland, are you able to depart from another city?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: we can depart from Toronto

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Gotham City is not a destination we travel to.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Are you interested in any other destinations?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: hmm what options would i have out of Toronto?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you be interested in Calgary?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: that would be nice

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I have a departure from Toronto to Calgary  on August 17 returning on August 24.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Does that work for you?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: No sorry i was planning on getting a tan this vacation.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Thanks, is there anywhere else?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text:
Thank you
is there anywhere else?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: How about a trip to Dominican Republic?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: it is quite cheap at this time of year.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: What options do you have available for me?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I have the el Mar hotel available in Punta Cana this week.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: That sounds interesting.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: how many stars does the hotel have?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: 2.5 stars.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: You would have to fly out of Melbourne though

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Ahh...maybe another time

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Hi I'd like to go to Caprica from Busan, between Sunday August 21, 2016 and Wednesday August 31, 2016

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: And what would be your maximum budget for this trip?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Actually it's unlimited for this trip

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: How many adults and how many children will be making this trip?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: 2 adults

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I have no trips to Caprica from Busan.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I do have a trip to Mannheim, Germany, one to Kingston , Canada, and another to Toronto Canada.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you like to select alternate dates or an alternate travel destination?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Do you have anything for San Antonio as a destination?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Yes, I do.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I have one for 8445.37 USD.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you like to book this package?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: The guest rating is 7.15/10 and there is free parking and free wifi.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Leaving Sunday, August 21st at 11:00 a.m. and returning Sunday, August 28th at 1:00 a.m.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Is breakfast included?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Yes, it is.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: That sounds great.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: 1:00 am return on Sunday August 28th is very early in the morning...

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you like to book this package?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Yes I would.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Thanks for your help.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Hey, i Want to go to St. Louis on the 17th of August

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: For how many days?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: I need to back by the 31st

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: What will your departure city be?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: I’m from Calgary

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I have a direct flight leaving from Calgary on August 18 and returning on August 28th.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Does that work for you?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Yes that sounds perfect may you please tell me about the destination place

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: It is the Glorious Cloak inn hotel in St. Louis.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: It has a 3-star rating.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: That sounds lavish, what type of flight would that be?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: You would be flying business class, for a grand total of only $1858.14

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Are there any possible flights with economy class?

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: I have a package at the Lunar whcih has a 5 star rating on an economy class flight on the same dates for $1558.00

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: that sounds even better.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: This deal includes free breakfast and free wifi.

utterances.speaker: SYS
utterances.text: Would you like me to book it for you?

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: Yes please, that sounds wonderful.

utterances.speaker: USR
utterances.text: thank you
